quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,"“Tâ-Sîn. Izi ndi Ayah (ndime) (za Qur’an buku lodzazidwa ndi zothandiza), ndiponso buku lofotokoza (chilichonse chauzimu ndi chamoyo wadziko)"
  27,2,“(Qur’an) nchiongoko ndi nkhani yabwino kwa okhulupirira
  27,3,"“Amene akupemphera Swala (zisanu, modzichepetsa ndi mokwaniritsa malamulo ake) ndi kumapereka Zakaat (m’nthawi yake), ndipo iwo ali ndi chitsimikizo champhamvu cha (moyo wa) tsiku la chimaliziro"
  27,4,"“Ndithu amene sakhulupirira za (moyo wa) tsiku la chimaliziro, tawakometsera zochita zoipa kukhala ngati zabwino; choncho iwo akungoyumbayumba (m’kusokera kwawo)"
  27,5,"“Iwowo ndiamene adzapeza chilango choipa; iwo tsiku lachimaliziro ngotayika zedi, (adzaonongeka ku Moto motheratu)"
  27,6,"“Ndipo ndithu iwe ukuphunzitsidwa Qur’an kuchokera kwa mwini nzeru zakuya, Wodziwa kwambiri"
  27,7,"“(Kumbuka) Mûsa pamene adauza banja lake (mkazi wake): “Ndithu ine ndaona moto; posachedwapa ndikubweretserani nkhani za kumeneko, kapena ndikubweretserani chikuni cha moto kuti inu muothe"
  27,8,"“Choncho pamene adaudzera (motowo) kudaitanidwa: “Wadalitsidwa yemwe ali m’moto ndi yemwe ali m’mphepete mwake; ndipo walemekezeka Allah Mbuye wa zolengedwa"
  27,9,"“E iwe Mûsa! Ndithu ine ndine Allah, Wamphamvu zoposa; Wanzeru zakuya"
  27,10,"“Ndipo ponya (pansi) ndodo yako! (Pamene adaiponya idasanduka njoka), tero pamene adaiwona ikugwedezeka (ndodo ija) ngati njoka, adatembenuka kuthawa, ndipo sadacheuke (kapena kudikira kuti amve mawu omvekawo): “E iwe Mûsa! Usaope. Ndithu Ine, saopa kwa Ine atumiki.”"
  27,11,"““Koma amene wadzichitira yekha zoipa, kenako nkusintha (pochita) zabwino pambuyo pa zoipa, (ndimkhululukira) pakuti Ine ndine Wokhululuka kwabasi, Wachifundo chambiri.”"
  27,12,"““Ndipo lowetsa dzanja lako palisani la mkanjo wako, ndipo lituluka lili loyera, (kuyera) kopanda matenda. (Ziwirizi) zili m’gulu la zododometsa zisanu ndi zinayi. Pita nazo kwa Farawo ndi anthu ake; ndithu iwo ndianthu otuluka m’chilamulo cha Allah.”"
  27,13,"“Tero pamene zidawadzera zizindikiro Zathu zosonyeza (kuti iye ndimtumiki wa Allah) adati: “Awa ndimatsenga woonekera.”"
  27,14,"“Ndipo adazitsutsa (zisonyezozo) mwachinyengo ndi modzikuza chikhalirecho mitima yawo idatsimikiza (kuti ndizoona zochokera kwa Allah); choncho, yang’ana adali bwanji malekezero a oononga"
  27,15,"“Ndipo ndithu Daud ndi Sulaiman tidawapatsa nzeru (zazikulu; adayamika Allah) adati: “Kuyamikidwa konse kwabwino nkwa Allah Yemwe watichitira ubwino kuposa ambiri mwa akapolo ake okhulupirira.”"
  27,16,"“Ndipo Sulaiman adalowa mmalo mwa Daud pa nzeru ndi uneneri ndipo (Sulaiman) adati: “E inu anthu! Ndithu taphunzitsidwa (mpaka tikudziwa) chiyankhulo cha mbalame, ndiponso tapatsidwa chilichonse; ndithu umenewu ndiubwino wopenyeka"
  27,17,"“Ndipo adasonkhanitsidwa kwa Sulaiman ankhondo ake ochokera m’ziwanda, anthu ndi mbalame, ndipo adawandandika m’magulumagulu"
  27,18,"“Kufikira pamene adadza pachigwa chanyelere, nyelere idanena (kuuza zinzake): “E inu nyelere, lowani m’nyumba zanu poopa kuti angakupondeni Sulaiman ndi magulu ake ankhondo pomwe iwo sakudziwa (za inu).”"
  27,19,"“Choncho adamwetulira, mosekelera chifukwa cha mawu ake aja (mawu a nyelere); ndipo (Sulaiman) adati: “E Mbuye wanga! Ndipatseni nyonga zakuti ndizithokozera mtendere wanu umene mwandidalitsa nawo pamodzi ndi makolo anga, ndi kuti ndizichita zabwino (zomwe) mukuziyanja; Kupyolera m’chifundo chanu, ndiponso ndilowetseni m’gulu la akapolo anu abwino.”"
  27,20,"“Ndipo adayamba kuyendera mbalame, adati: “Kodi bwanji sindikumuona Huduhudu? Kapena ali m’gulu la amene pano palibe?”"
  27,21,"““Ndithu ndimulanga chilango chokhwima, kapena ndimzinga (ndimdula khosi) pokhapokha andibweletsere umboni womveka (wosonyeza kuti adachoka pazifukwa zomveka).”"
  27,22,"“Choncho (Hudhud) sadakhalitse nthawi yaitali; ndipo adati (kwa Sulaiman): “Ndatulukira zomwe iwe sudazitulukire, ndipo ndakubweletsera nkhani yotsimikizika kuchokera ku Saba.”"
  27,23,"““Ndithu ine ndapeza mkazi akuwalamulira (anthu a ku dziko la Saba), ndipo wapatsidwa chilichonse; ndiponso ali ndi chimpando chachifumu chachikulu.”"
  27,24,"““Ndampeza iye ndi anthu ake akulambira dzuwa kusiya Allah; ndipo satana wawakometsera zochita zawo zoipa; choncho wawatsekereza ku njira yolungama, tero sadaongoke.”"
  27,25,““Kuti asamlambire Allah yemwe amatulutsa zobisika kumwamba ndi pansi; ndipo akudziwa zimene mukubisa ndi zimene muonetsa poyera.”
  27,26,““Allah! Palibe wina wopembedzedwa mwachoona koma Iye basi; Mbuye wa Arsh (Mpando wachifumu) waukulu.”